m/apps/1079230/extras/e02404036c49191e0432de0cae4ca49a.mp4?t=1770992338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>建立并且改造你的基地，用具有自我意识的完美机器来打造更加精美的装备，构建电路网络，省却人工的烦恼<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079230/extras/6cd3de1d9410380abade8d5c7340e128.poster.avif?t=1770992338\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079230/extras/6cd3de1d9410380abade8d5c7340e128.webm?t=1770992338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079230/extras/6cd3de1d9410380abade8d5c7340e128.mp4?t=1770992338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>快节奏的地空战<br></li><li>大量装饰品和机器可供建造并且自动化你的基地<br></li><li>情感丰富的背景音乐和生动的视觉效果<br></li><li>总能带来新发现的程序生成的地图<br></li><li>超过100种独特的武器和装备来满足各种玩家的游戏风格<br></li><li>支持本地多人与好友一同游玩<br></li><li>完全的控制器、操作板和键盘支持</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079230/extras/427494df1f71d2842f78c50f163852ae.poster.avif?t=1770992338\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079230/extras/427494df1f71d2842f78c50f163852ae.webm?t=1770992338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079230/extras/427494df1f71d2842f78c50f163852ae.mp4?t=1770992338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
